msgctxt "experience.datadome.title"
msgid "Senior iOS Software Engineer"
msgstr "資深 iOS 軟體工程師"

msgctxt "experience.datadome.date"
msgid "Sept 2022 - Present"
msgstr "2022年9月 - 至今"

msgctxt "experience.datadome.bullet.1"
msgid ""
"Lead a team of 3 mobile developers, owning the full lifecycle of 14 SDKs "
"across iOS, Android, React Native, Flutter, and KMM for DataDome's bot "
"protection platform, used by clients such as TripAdvisor, SoundCloud, and "
"The New York Times"
msgstr ""
"領導 3 人行動開發團隊，負責 DataDome 機器人防護平台上橫跨 iOS、Android、React Native、Flutter 與 KMM 共"
" 14 個 SDK 的完整生命週期，客戶包括 TripAdvisor、SoundCloud 與 The New York Times"

msgctxt "experience.datadome.bullet.2"
msgid ""
"Architect and maintain the iOS SDK in Swift (+ others in their respective "
"technologies), integrated by enterprise clients for real-time bot and fraud "
"detection"
msgstr "以 Swift 設計並維護 iOS SDK（其餘平台則以各自技術實作），供企業客戶整合以進行即時機器人與詐欺偵測"

msgctxt "experience.datadome.bullet.3"
msgid ""
"Reduced customer support tickets by 50% through improved SDK documentation, "
"simpler APIs, and comprehensive unit and E2E test coverage"
msgstr "透過改善 SDK 文件、簡化 API 以及完整的單元測試與端對端測試覆蓋，將客戶支援工單減少 50%"

msgctxt "experience.datadome.bullet.4"
msgid ""
"Drive code reviews, technical decisions, and release planning for the mobile"
" SDK team"
msgstr "主導行動 SDK 團隊的程式碼審查、技術決策與版本發布規劃"

msgctxt "experience.datadome.bullet.5"
msgid ""
"Implement CI/CD pipelines ensuring reliable delivery across all platforms"
msgstr "建置 CI/CD 流程，確保在所有平台上穩定可靠地交付"

msgctxt "experience.sightcall.title"
msgid "Senior iOS Engineer"
msgstr "資深 iOS 工程師"

msgctxt "experience.sightcall.date"
msgid "March 2021 - Sept 2022"
msgstr "2021年3月 - 2022年9月"

msgctxt "experience.sightcall.bullet.1"
msgid ""
"Developed the iOS SDK for SightCall's AR-powered remote visual assistance "
"platform, used by enterprise clients such as Sony, Ford, and GE Healthcare"
msgstr ""
"開發 SightCall 以擴增實境為核心的遠端視覺協助平台 iOS SDK，供 Sony、Ford 與 GE Healthcare 等企業客戶使用"

msgctxt "experience.sightcall.bullet.2"
msgid ""
"Built real-time AR annotation features with ARKit, allowing users to place "
"3D markers, drawings, and measurements on live video streams"
msgstr "以 ARKit 建置即時 AR 標註功能，讓使用者可在即時視訊串流上放置 3D 標記、繪圖與測量"

msgctxt "experience.sightcall.bullet.3"
msgid ""
"Integrated Core ML for on-device object detection and annotation during live"
" video sessions"
msgstr "整合 Core ML，於即時視訊期間在裝置端進行物件偵測與標註"

msgctxt "experience.sightcall.bullet.4"
msgid ""
"Migrated the legacy Objective-C codebase to Swift, modernizing the SDK "
"architecture"
msgstr "將既有的 Objective-C 程式碼遷移至 Swift，現代化 SDK 架構"

msgctxt "experience.sightcall.bullet.5"
msgid "Built CI/CD pipelines with Bitrise, automating the release process"
msgstr "以 Bitrise 建置 CI/CD 流程，自動化發布流程"

msgctxt "experience.mention.title"
msgid "iOS Engineer"
msgstr "iOS 工程師"

msgctxt "experience.mention.date"
msgid "Sept 2015 - March 2021"
msgstr "2015年9月 - 2021年3月"

msgctxt "experience.mention.bullet.1"
msgid "Sole iOS developer responsible for the full Mention iOS application"
msgstr "唯一的 iOS 開發者，負責整個 Mention iOS 應用程式"

msgctxt "experience.mention.bullet.2"
msgid ""
"Led complete migration from Objective-C to Swift, improving code "
"maintainability and developer velocity"
msgstr "主導從 Objective-C 到 Swift 的完整遷移，提升程式碼可維護性與開發效率"

msgctxt "experience.mention.bullet.3"
msgid ""
"Extracted business logic into a reusable SDK, separating front-end and "
"business layers to prepare for future applications"
msgstr "將商業邏輯抽離為可重用的 SDK，分離前端與商業邏輯層，為未來的應用程式做準備"

msgctxt "experience.mention.bullet.4"
msgid ""
"Built a custom GraphQL implementation to avoid Apollo's heavy code "
"generation, alongside REST APIs and real-time WebSocket features"
msgstr "自行實作 GraphQL 以避免 Apollo 繁重的程式碼產生，並搭配 REST API 與即時 WebSocket 功能"

msgctxt "experience.mention.bullet.5"
msgid ""
"Reduced app crash rate by 30% through systematic debugging, memory "
"management improvements, and crash reporting analysis"
msgstr "透過系統化除錯、記憶體管理改善與當機報告分析，將應用程式當機率降低 30%"

msgctxt "experience.mention.bullet.6"
msgid ""
"Recruited the Android developer, designed Kotlin technical challenges, and "
"mentored them on mobile best practices and architecture"
msgstr "招募 Android 開發者，設計 Kotlin 技術測驗，並在行動開發最佳實務與架構上提供指導"

msgctxt "experience.rotormatch.title"
msgid "Co-Founder & Software Engineer (part-time)"
msgstr "共同創辦人暨軟體工程師（兼職）"

msgctxt "experience.rotormatch.date"
msgid "Feb 2016 - Jan 2020"
msgstr "2016年2月 - 2020年1月"

msgctxt "experience.rotormatch.bullet.1"
msgid "Co-founded a drone racing event technology company"
msgstr "共同創辦一家無人機競速賽事科技公司"

msgctxt "experience.rotormatch.bullet.2"
msgid ""
"Built a race timing system: an embedded system for signal capture, a Swift "
"app for data reading and backend sync (custom UDP library), and a web app "
"for the race control center"
msgstr ""
"建置賽事計時系統：用於訊號擷取的嵌入式系統、用於資料讀取與後端同步的 Swift 應用程式（自製 UDP 函式庫），以及賽事指揮中心的網頁應用程式"

msgctxt "experience.rotormatch.bullet.3"
msgid "Live-streamed to multiple platforms including our own RotorTV"
msgstr "同步直播至多個平台，包括我們自有的 RotorTV"

msgctxt "experience.rotormatch.bullet.4"
msgid "Event planning platform, ticket booking platform"
msgstr "賽事規劃平台、票務預訂平台"

msgctxt "experience.rotormatch.bullet.5"
msgid "NFC/RFID integration and reverse engineering of custom protocols"
msgstr "NFC／RFID 整合與自訂協定的逆向工程"

